  "keyFeatures": [
    "360° equirectangular panorama rendering using Three.js",
    "Multiple adapter support: cubemap, tiled panoramas, video panoramas, dual-fisheye",
    "Rich plugin system with 14+ official plugins",
    "Markers plugin for points of interest with tooltips and descriptions",
    "Virtual tour plugin for multi-panorama navigation",
    "Gallery plugin for panorama browsing",
    "Autorotate, gyroscope, and stereo (VR) viewing modes",
    "Interactive map and plan plugins for navigation",
    "TypeScript support with full type definitions",
    "EventTarget API with strongly-typed events",
    "CDN and npm installation support",
    "Framework integration guides (React, Vue, etc.)"
  ],
